{"tid":782872,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"Windows 檔案實體化布袋上市！遊日平價創意手信","createTime":"2018-08-17T06:06:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-18T08:43:54.000Z","uid":125073,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"71ca0d2808f5489e1426e700214db03e1bfbf61d","tid":782872,"uid":125073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T06:06:27.000Z","msg":"雖然 Windows 系統已經換了很多代，但作爲電腦常用的系統之一，大家見到 Windows 的電腦 Icon 總有一種親切感。所以，日本有公司就推出了以 Windows 檔案圖案爲概念的創意收納布袋！<br />\n<br />\n這個「PCアイコンポーチ（PC Icon Pouch）」系列一共有 6 款，分別是「PDF」、「Music」、「壓縮 File」、「垃圾筒」、「Xcel」 以及見到就頭痕的「Program 強制結束」，每個都是布製附有拉鏈，能夠收納文具、數據線等小物，十分方便。<br />\n<br />\n雖然這個系列惡搞成份居多，但就十分便宜，一款只需要 200 円（約 HK $14），入手全套亦不會心痛。到日本旅遊的朋友，買來送給朋友當手信也是一個不錯的選擇呢！<br />\n<br />\nSource：<a href=\"http://nlab.itmedia.co.jp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnlab.itmedia.co.jp&d=0ME6ik%2BdFVAdTzaqX0vXmU%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=4958f43a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">nlab.itmedia.co.jp</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有冇巴絲打可以幫手代購番黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"411dea90b47e66a1c154ab16d34b3394f4f2190a","tid":782872,"uid":63588,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T06:37:06.000Z","msg":"圖都無張 link又唔識貼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80586ffd50ca85ddf90430777583343cce3eb7dc","tid":782872,"uid":125073,"like":2,"dislike":25,"score":-23,"quote":{"pid":"411dea90b47e66a1c154ab16d34b3394f4f2190a","tid":782872,"uid":63588,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T06:37:06.000Z","msg":"圖都無張 link又唔識貼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"